quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  12,7,In Joseph his frater ibi est lessons seekers
  12,8,They dictus Joseph his frater favored noster patris nos est majoritatatis! Indeed noster patris est far astray
  12,9,kill Joseph banish eum ut vos get some attention ex tuus patris! Afterwards vos est righteous people
  12,10,de them dictus non kill Joseph; throw eum abyss bene! Perhaps some caravan pick eum hoc est quod vos decide perfecit
  12,11,They dictus Noster patris vos non trust nos Joseph? Nos take bonus care de eum
  12,12,Send eum nos cras run play Nos protect eum
  12,13,He dictus ego injuria lest vos iit eum tunc wolf devour eum dum vos non watching eum
  12,14,They dictus Indeed wolf devours eum multus de nos circiter tunc nos est really losers
  12,15,When they iit eum ac unanimously decided throw eum into abyss bene nos inspired eum Some feria vos tell them totus hoc dum they non habet idea
  12,16,They advenit their patris in the et weeping
  12,17,They dictus Noster patris nos iit genus each alius sinister Joseph noster equipment wolf devoured eum! Vos nunquam believe nos et nos telling truth
  12,18,They produced his shirt fake blood it He dictus Indeed vos conspired each alius to commit certain scheme totus ego perfecit est resort to quiet patience! Maius DEUS help me in the face de tuus conspiracy
  12,19,caravan passed soon sent their waterer! He let his bucket tunc dictus Quam lucky ibi est garcio hic! They took eum along merchandise DEUS est fully aware de quod they perfecit
  12,20,They sold eum cheap price - ut few dirhams - Pro they non habet any need pro eum